RELATIONSHIP TO FREE VERSION

NetStacks Pro is the commercial, enterprise edition of NetStacks.

The free NetStacks version is available under a separate Non-Commercial License
at: https://github.com/netstacks/netstacks

Key differences:
  - Free version: Non-commercial use only, community support
  - Pro version: Commercial use permitted, enterprise features, professional support
